PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776103864
OL,3,COver 60% of Australian children still
OL,4,Cusing social media despite under-16s
OL,5,Cban
OL,7,FThe UK government is currently
OL,8,Fconsulting on whether or not to
OL,9,Fimplement similar measures in the UK,
OL,10,Fand a band has already been backed by
OL,11,Fthe House of Lords.
OL,13,FAs well as looking into the pros and
OL,14,Fcons of blocking young teens from
OL,15,Fsocial media apps, measures being
OL,16,Fconsidered by lawmakers include
OL,17,Fcurfews and restricting access to
OL,18,Faddictive features.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
