PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776103864
OL,3,COver 60% of Australian children still
OL,4,Cusing social media despite under-16s
OL,5,Cban
OL,7,FThe Molly Rose Foundation is a UK-
OL,8,Fbased suicide prevention charity set
OL,9,Fup in memory of Molly Russell, who was
OL,10,F14 when she took her own life after
OL,11,Fviewing harmful content online.
OL,13,FThe charity is calling for the UK
OL,14,Fgovernment to strengthen regulation
OL,15,Faround tech firms to help protect
OL,16,Fyoung people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776103864
OL,3,COver 60% of Australian children still
OL,4,Cusing social media despite under-16s
OL,5,Cban
OL,7,FAndy Burrows, Chief Executive of MRF,
OL,8,Fsaid: "These results raise major
OL,9,Fquestions about the effectiveness of
OL,10,FAustralia's social media ban and show
OL,11,Fit would be a high stakes gamble for
OL,12,Fthe UK to follow suit now.
OL,14,F"Parents and children deserve better
OL,15,Fthan a flawed ban that delivers a
OL,16,Ffalse sense of safety that quickly
OL,17,Funravels."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776103864
OL,3,COver 60% of Australian children still
OL,4,Cusing social media despite under-16s
OL,5,Cban
OL,7,FIan Russell, Chair of MRF, added:
OL,8,F"Parents are united that change is
OL,9,Fneeded to protect children from
OL,10,Fappalling harm online and it is
OL,11,Fcrucial we see effective action that
OL,12,Fdelivers the safety and wellbeing
OL,13,Fimprovements we are crying out for.
OL,15,F"The prime minister is right that
OL,16,Ftackling addictive and dangerous
OL,17,Fdesign choices is key. He must now put
OL,18,Fwords into action with strengthened
OL,19,Fregulation that cuts to the heart of
OL,20,Fbusiness models that put profit over
OL,21,Fsafety.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776103864
OL,3,COver 60% of Australian children still
OL,4,Cusing social media despite under-16s
OL,5,Cban
OL,7,F"Keir Starmer has the chance to make
OL,8,Fthe UK a world leader in online safety
OL,9,Fby following the evidence with robust
OL,10,Fnew laws that give parents what they
OL,11,Fare rightly demanding.
OL,13,F"The cost is too high to get this
OL,14,Fwrong by rushing into an Australia-
OL,15,Fstyle ban that offers the perception
OL,16,Fof security but is letting children
OL,17,Fdown in practice."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
