OL,3,COver 60% of Australian children still
OL,4,Cusing social media despite under-16s
OL,5,Cban
OL,7,FEuropean countries such as Greece,
OL,8,FAustria and Denmark have all suggested
OL,9,Fthey plan on banning social media for
OL,10,Fyounger teens.
OL,12,FITV News contacted Meta, YouTube and
OL,13,FTikTok for comment.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
